  <brief_title>Comparison of a Laser Keratome to a Mechanical Microkeratome</brief_title>
  <official_title>Comparison of INTRALASE® to AMADEUS™ Microkeratome</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Medical University of South Carolina</agency>
      <agency_class>Other</agency_class>
    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>Medical University of South Carolina</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study was to evaluate the performance of the INTRALASE®, a laser keratome
      which creates a corneal flap, and compare it to a mechanical microkeratome (Amadeus™). Our
      hypothesis is that there is no difference between the 2 devices.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
